node.title: NT records no new COVID-19 cases
node.alt: Chief Minister Michael Gunner is standing in front of a microphone with a serious expression. Behind him is the Australian flag.
node.description: The Northern Territory has recorded no new COVID-19 cases overnight, Chief Minister Michael Gunner says.
node.content: ["The Northern Territory has recorded\u00a0no\u00a0new COVID-19 cases overnight, Chief Minister Michael Gunner says.", "The cluster between Katherine and Robinson River still\u00a0stands at 19 cases, all of whom are Aboriginal Territorians.", "\u201cThis is good news, but it is not a day to get ahead of ourselves.\u00a0We will not assume it means that we have trapped the virus,\u201d Mr Gunner said.", "\u201cThis is Delta. This is in large, vulnerable households. We're not out of the woods.\u00a0", "\u201cThe next day or two remain crucial.\u201d", "Mr Gunner said the Northern Territory\u00a0government was still waiting on tests to return from\u00a0Robinson River cases and some close contacts were still waiting to be tested or to get\u00a0their results.\u00a0", "He said not all close contacts had been located and there would also be re-testing for contacts who had returned a negative result.\u00a0", "\u201cThere's also a strong chance of close contacts who have tested negative returning a positive test in coming days,\u201d he said.\u00a0", "\u201cWe still have lots of testing and tracing work to do, but things are looking more positive.\u201d", "Mr Gunner announced just one close contact new exposure site, the BP service station in Katherine, on November 13, between 2:40 and\u00a04pm.", "In total, 384 close contacts have been identified, 288 of whom had been successfully contacted and are isolating and 201 have\u00a0returned a negative test.", "Investigations into the MacFarlane Primary School site are ongoing, Mr Gunner said.\u00a0", "\u201cThe close contacts from that site [have\u00a0now been]\u00a0identified as 38 \u2014\u00a010 adults, 28 children,\u201d Mr Gunner said.\u00a0", "\u201cMost of these close contacts have been contacted, we still have work to do to contact the last five.\"", "Mr Gunner said genomic sequencing for the cluster was expected back this afternoon or tomorrow morning.\u00a0", "\"This will be extremely important as it will confirm if clusters one and two are linked,\"\u00a0he said.\u00a0", "\"Our belief remains that they are most likely linked.", "\"Until we have this link, we cannot assume.\"", "More to come."]
